lead_paragraph: Melo Trimble scored 20 points, Jake Layman added 16 points and 10 rebounds, and No. 8 Maryland made six free throws in the final 25 seconds to beat Ohio State 66-61 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Trimble Leads No. 8 Maryland Past Ohio State 66-61
